_sText:
V4.
Fixed buyzone
Added 50% more to the top level of the map.
Harder for cts to camp.
Buildcubemaps.

The map before was a little cramped with 50 players, this caused lag on the server I played this on.
Now the top floor has another area, im hoping a large number of players will choose this area so that the amount of players in one place will be reduced.
My graphics card is quite poor (x1050 ati) and on this map I can get upto 220fps if looking at the clouds lol, average is around 70fps with a better card Im sure you will see some good fps figures.

Maps pretty simple I hope for fast rounds where the zombie wins all the time :D :P

Hunt Hunt Hunt!!!
